Hi, my name is Adrian, but you can call me Adik for short. I live in Poland.

This channel is my own playground, you can expect to see anything here, for example:
Reaction videos, where i give you my opinion on material featured in them
Streams, where you can watch me live, while i'm doing anything, from playing video games, to making some quizes, to just talking with my subscribers

I record my videos using camera from my Smartphone (live footage) and "OBS Studio" to record everything on my computer.
I edit my videos in Adobe Premiere Pro
